      <title>共产党中国压制有关台湾选举的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/communist-china-clamps-down-on-chatter-about-taiwan-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国执政的共产党正在限制有关台湾选举的互联网讨论，这表明北京对民主活动感到不满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/communist-china-clamps-down-on-chatter-about-taiwan-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 06:27:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电视节目为英国邮局丑闻伸张正义</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/it-took-a-tv-show-to-bring-justice-in-uk-s-post-office-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西玛·米斯拉（Seema Misra）因从她在伦敦西南部小镇经营的邮局盗窃而被错误地定罪，当时她已经怀孕了。七个月后，她在医院生下孩子，其中四个月在监狱里度过，她戴着脚踝标签，用于监视被释放的罪犯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/it-took-a-tv-show-to-bring-justice-in-uk-s-post-office-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科摩罗领导人在抵制选举的呼声中寻求新任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/comoros-leader-seeks-new-term-amid-calls-for-election-boycott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科摩罗总统阿扎利·阿苏马尼希望在周日举行的选举中继续担任这个印度洋国家的领导人五年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/comoros-leader-seeks-new-term-amid-calls-for-election-boycott</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾总统三人竞选投票结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-01-13/taiwan-presidential-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024 年 1 月 13 日星期六，选民在台湾台北的一个投票站排队。台湾选民即将前往投票站，这场选举将决定台湾未来几年与华盛顿和北京的关系，并影响该地区安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/live-blog/2024-01-13/taiwan-presidential-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 04:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔总统候选人 Ousmane Sonko 被禁止参加 2024 年投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/senegal-presidential-hopeful-ousmane-sonko-barred-from-2024-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《太阳报》报道，根据宪法委员会周五公布的初步候选人名单，塞内加尔主要反对派政治家奥斯曼·桑科在下个月的总统选举中被淘汰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/senegal-presidential-hopeful-ousmane-sonko-barred-from-2024-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 03:56:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国在更广泛的袭击后一天对也门发动新的袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/us-launches-new-strike-in-yemen-against-houthi-radar-facility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国周五对胡塞叛军的雷达设施发动了新的空袭，据称这是对也门早先的一次袭击的后续袭击，旨在削弱该组织瞄准红海商业航运的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-13/us-launches-new-strike-in-yemen-against-houthi-radar-facility</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 02:04:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和英国如何攻击胡塞武装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-s-clear-message-how-us-uk-came-to-attack-the-houthis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1月1日上午，美国总统乔·拜登在圣克罗伊岛度假时召集了国家安全团队会议。几周来，要求对伊朗支持的胡塞武装分子采取军事行动的压力不断增大，因为他们持续袭击红海航运。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/biden-s-clear-message-how-us-uk-came-to-attack-the-houthis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 21:39:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾选举新领导人受到世界密切关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/taiwan-picks-new-leader-in-election-closely-watched-by-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾选民已经完成了选举投票，这场选举将决定台湾未来几年与华盛顿和北京的关系，并影响地区安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/taiwan-picks-new-leader-in-election-closely-watched-by-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布林肯在台湾选举之际会见中国高级官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/blinken-meets-top-chinese-official-on-cusp-of-taiwan-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，国务卿安东尼·布林肯会见了中国一位高级外交政策官员，两国正在努力重建近年来因紧张局势加剧而中断的联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/blinken-meets-top-chinese-official-on-cusp-of-taiwan-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 17:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸军政府表示已与叛军达成停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/myanmar-s-junta-says-it-reached-cease-fire-deal-with-rebels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军政府表示，在中国支持的谈判后，他们与叛乱分子达成了临时停火协议，有可能结束两个多月的战斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/myanmar-s-junta-says-it-reached-cease-fire-deal-with-rebels</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 09:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
